{%- comment -%}
  ============================================================
  MAIN 404 — página de erro "não encontrado"
  ============================================================

  O QUE FAZ:
  Tela exibida quando a URL não existe (erro 404). Mostra o código
  "404", título e subtexto, um campo de busca e um link para voltar
  à home, ajudando o visitante a se reorientar.

  ONDE É USADA:
  Template 404 (páginas inexistentes).

  PRINCIPAIS PARTES:
  - Formulário de busca aponta para routes.search_url (GET, name="q")
  - Link routes.root_url volta para a home
  - Textos via i18n (general.404.*, general.search.*)
  - Sem settings no schema

  OBSERVAÇÕES:
  No mobile a busca empilha (flex-direction: column).
{%- endcomment -%}

<section class="notfound page-width" data-section-id="{{ section.id }}">
  <div class="notfound__inner">
    <p class="notfound__code" aria-hidden="true">404</p>
    <h1 class="notfound__title">{{ 'general.404.title' | t }}</h1>
    <p class="notfound__subtext">{{ 'general.404.subtext' | t }}</p>

    <form action="{{ routes.search_url }}" method="get" role="search" class="notfound__search">
      <label class="visually-hidden" for="Search404-{{ section.id }}">
        {{ 'general.search.search' | t }}
      </label>
      <input
        type="search"
        class="field__input notfound__search-input"
        id="Search404-{{ section.id }}"
        name="q"
        placeholder="{{ 'general.search.placeholder' | t }}"
        spellcheck="false"
        autocomplete="off"
      >
      <button type="submit" class="button notfound__search-submit">
        {{ 'general.search.submit' | t }}
      </button>
    </form>

    <a href="{{ routes.root_url }}" class="notfound__home">
      {{ 'general.continue_shopping' | t }}
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .notfound {
    min-height: 60vh;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding-top: var(--spacing-sections, 40px);
    padding-bottom: var(--spacing-sections, 40px);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .notfound__inner {
    max-width: 520px;
  }

  .notfound__code {
    font-family: var(--font-heading-family);
    font-size: clamp(4rem, 12vw, 8rem);
    line-height: 1;
    color: var(--color-accent);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .notfound__title {
    font-size: var(--f6);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .notfound__subtext {
    font-size: var(--f2);
    opacity: 0.75;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }

  .notfound__search {
    display: flex;
    gap: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  .notfound__search-input {
    flex: 1;
  }

  .notfound__home {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-decoration: underline;
  }

  @media screen and (max-width: 1000px) {
    .notfound__title {
      font-size: var(--f5);
    }

    .notfound__search {
      flex-direction: column;
    }
  }
</style>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "t:sections.main_404.name",
  "tag": "section",
  "class": "section-main-404",
  "settings": []
}
{% endschema %}
